Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:32.53,Sorey,,0,0,0,,能站起來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:41.63,Alisha,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.61,Alisha,,0,0,0,,看來勞你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:45.73,Alisha,,0,0,0,,你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:47.67,Sorey,,0,0,0,,我是史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:49.03,Sorey,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:50.53,Alisha,,0,0,0,,史雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:57.79,Alisha,,0,0,0,,史雷…
